                    <div class="integration" id="integration1">
                        <h2 class="integration__title">Salesforce cloud <a href="#integration__nav" class="totop"><i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i></a></h2>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-4">
                                <div class="integration__img"><img alt="Salesforce Cloud " src="https://d1b89zc79exfxt.cloudfront.net/img/integration-img13.png"/></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-8">
                                <p>We are built on the Salesforce platform, and we want you to get the premium experience Salesforce gives to its users. We’re talking speed, security, advanced features and broader opportunities for growth.</p>

                                <p>Our Salesforce cloud integrations feature the best cloud tools Salesforce has to offer, including but not limited to Service cloud, IoT cloud, Analytics Cloud, App Cloud, Community Cloud, and Marketing Cloud. </p>
                                    
                                <p>These services change the way you see cloud technology today. They help you get work done remarkably faster and also perform tasks that would require highly paid experts to normally do.</p>
                                    
                                <p>We are giving you the Salesforce Cloud applications to help boost your business in a productive way. Never before has this been provided in a property management system.
                                    </p>
