                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-8">
                                <p>Control who enters where.</p>

                                <p>Booking Ninjas offers integrations that enable you to control who has access to specific places in your property. By that, you can increase security and create a reasonable sense of safety in your property. Guests like that.</p>
                                    
                                <p>It’s a requirement for most hotels to recognize their top patrons. By access control, you can give VIP privileges, granting exclusive access to your high-value customers, honoring them for their valued patronage.</p>
                                    
                                <p>Our biometric scans integrations also offer a quality type of security clearance, giving your top clients the very impressive privacy they deserve.</p>
                                
